data.description: *BUYER AND AGENT INCENTIVES!!! MOTIVATED SELLER* Extraordinary View of Liberty Lake from the living rooms wall of windows. Wake up to the same view in the primary suite. This 2 bedroom, 2 bath (4-Unit) condo features a spacious gallery kitchen with newer appliances, pull out cabinets, large pantry and new lighting.  New flooring in the hallway, dining, living room, kitchen and laundry area all on the main floor. Spacious primary bath has double vanities, new sinks and all new lighting, closets and Jacuzzi jetted tub. Built in office area as well as storage galore in unit. Enjoy all the conveniences of living close-in, while living in this secluded hideaway nestled among the pines with dramatic lake & mountain views!  The HOA provides access to the shared Wicomico Beach in addition to lawn and grounds care, snow removal, sewer, water, garbage, and building insurance. Schedule your tour today!
